name: Find My Cheese Web Player
description:
Find my Cheese! Alpha Release

A simple puzzle game inspired by Castle Mouse by Pizmo Games©. 

Help the mouse find its cheese to complete the level.  

Animals scare certain adjacent other animals, in order: 

  • Elephant
  • Lion
  • Bear
  • Dog
  • Cat
  • Mouse

And the Mouse in turn scares the Elephant.

Features:

  • A dozen levels of increasing difficulty! 
  •  Music can be disabled
  • 3 camera angles
